{
  "texts": [
    "Knowledge from practice ultimately returns to practice.",
    "The research of complex systems requires multilevel and multi-perspective methods and cognition.Statistical physics is a bridge between micro and macro scales, and the kinetic theory is a bridge between micro and macro descriptions of fluid systems.",
    "Coarsegrained modeling is a basic means to grasp the main contradiction according to the research needs of nonequilibrium statistical physics.",
    "The related study on Boltzmann equation is a relatively mature part in the theory of kinetics.",
    "In the context of fluid dynamics, \"cross-scale\" typically refers to scaling across Knudsen numbers.Complex flows are typically associated with unsteady behavior, but the study of steady-state behavior is also an important aspect."
  ]
}